Made with real 2mm thickened steel and 50mm thickened multi-triangle structure;
With unique connections, the seat and handlebar will keep stable during cycling;
Widened stabilizers and steel cranks, heavy-duty and sturdy;
With all of these features, this exercise bike can support 300lbs, about 136kg.

