Product Description
How to Connect App? 
Device Name: DMASUN-8732D Bike 
1. Check whether the bike equipment is equipped with batteries? (included in the package), the device is located at the left crank; 
2. Make sure your smartphone or tablet device enabled; 
3. Start cycling bike and wait for equipment initialization; 
4. Open the "KINOMAP", "SPAX" or "ZWIFT" application on your smartphone or tablet; 
5. Follow the instructions in the application to start using the bike with the device connection function; 
6. Search for available devices and select "DMASUN-8732D Bike" from the list of available devices.

